Subject: [PATCH 19/19] web-app: buttonify About dialog links with
 settings-style buttons

Replace the plain text links in the About dialog (Delta Chat website,
GitHub, Imprint) with SettingsIconButton rows, matching the Settings
view. External web links carry an open_in_new indicator to signal they
leave the app; Imprint (a local page) does not. Adds buttons for the
SlothfulChat GitHub repo and the published changelog (GitHub releases).
---
